    <rigor-reason>This task produces the project's primary deliverable. Decision-grade synthesis affects how all future Spaarke AI projects approach Agent Framework. Quality bar matches docs/assessments/bff-ai-extraction-assessment-2026-05-20.md. Runs adr-check + code-review at Step 9.5.</rigor-reason>
