    <criterion>§10 Sources appendix tables every primary source URL + fetched date + referencing sections</criterion>
    <criterion>Length 800-1500 lines (or more if analysis warrants)</criterion>
    <criterion>adr-check + code-review both run at Step 9.5</criterion>
    <criterion>Document is in declarative tone — uncertainty lives in §8, not the body</criterion>
